headline: American Outdoor Brands, ThredUp, Paramount, Wynn Resorts, and Steven Madden Stocks Trade Down, What You Need To Know
summary: A number of stocks fell in the afternoon session after worries over worsening trade relations with China were triggered by critical comments from President Donald Trump.
